#GRAPHIC DESIGN WORKS

## New Logo for CAL FIRE San Luis Obispo Unit, Division 6 
This is the new logo for the CAL FIRE SLU Pre-Fire Division (Division 6)

![New Division 6 Pre-Fire Logo](http://i1301.photobucket.com/albums/ag102/takashiabiko/Div6Logo_JPEG_zps3xztkejl.jpg~original)

## One Less Spark, One Less Wildfire Campaign 
This is a public banner for CAL FIRE San Luis Obispo's "One Less Spark, One Less Wildfire" campaign.  The design was customized from graphic elements that were made available by the Califronia Wildland Fire Coordinating Group (preventwildfireca.org).  

![One Less Spark, One Less Wildfire](http://i1301.photobucket.com/albums/ag102/takashiabiko/OneLessSpark_300dpi_zpsemssyumc.jpg~original)

The banner is displayed on eight SLO County RTA buses during the years 2014 and 2015. The photo below is an example of one of the banners.
![One Less Spark, One Less Wildfire](http://i1301.photobucket.com/albums/ag102/takashiabiko/20140505_RTA_BusAd_Pic_zps9c8qt8oa.jpg)
